{{#> base}}
  <div class="content-box">
    <h1>What to Expect</h1>

    <p>
      Each student at CoderDojo is different and works at their own pace. Software development and creative fields cover <em>such</em> a broad range of topics - ranging from animal sprites all the way to the digital logic of zeroes and ones. The mastery guide below is just that - <em>a guide</em>.
    </p>

    <p>
      Each programming concept below is designed to take a day, but it might not take you all day. Everyone moves at their own pace, so do you! We'll be there to support you along the way.
    </p>
  </div>

